  "body": "It's now possible in 2.2.x to use the `--wait` flag to [wait for deploys](https://github.com/kubernetes/helm/issues/1805) to be ready which is a great addition especially for various CI/CD scenarios.\r\n\r\nHow feasible would it be to add the same to `helm init` with reference specifically to Tiller and it being ready to serve? Same premise as waiting for Charts to be ready but with Tiller itself to be installed/upgraded.",
